data.title: Barton announces president’s and dean’s lists for spring
data.meta_description: Barton College's Centennial Alumni Bell Tower is a landmark on campus. Drew C. Wilson | Times file photo Barton College named 97 full-time undergraduate students to the president’s list and 424 full-time undergraduate students to the dean’s list for the spring semester. President’s list students compiled a perfect 4.0 grade point average; dean’s list students
data.text:
Barton College named 97 full-time undergraduate students to the president’s list and 424 full-time undergraduate students to the dean’s list for the spring semester. President’s list students compiled a perfect 4.0 grade point average; dean’s list students achieved a grade point average of 3.3 or better on a 4-point scale.
